channel.title: V0id-Pkz v3 - Updates -
channel.description:
Well guys, here is the updates for both client and source of v0id-pkz v3 from v2
[b][u]Client and Source:[/u][/b]
[ul][*]New 474 Tool Kit Interface (100%) [*]100% Prayer [*]No more commands; only ::pickup and ::switch [*]New Specs [*]Areas have been updated, like new shops and etc [*]Removed all Music on Client, but one; faster DLing now [*]Wildy levels fixed [*]Lunar Interface added [*]Leveling up is faster [*]Music JFrame now on below of client [*]Training is slower now [*]SYIpkpker blocker [*]and etc[/ul]
[u][b]Removed[/b][/u]
[b]Source:[/b]
[ul][*]Most Pk areas [*]teleing commands [*]A lot of waste of coding, lagged server [*]etc[/ul]
[u][b]Client:[/b][/u]
[ul][*]Music, but one [*]Removed any extra graphics [*]Removed a lot of jframe buttons [*]and etc[/ul]
Picture: [img]http://img24.imageshack.us/img24/5323/nulln.png[/img]
Videos:
Dragon Bow Spec - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PGvOX_t4FQY New Interface - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QhvwJMbu-Sg Emote Interface - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y472Ec8DSIQ Range - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0nVyAR8CVCE 100 % - Prayer - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i0vENemttjk Fixed wily levels - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FwhgCMop4zk New Tool Kit Interface - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCS5dh4xUWc
-Done-
